dc_description_s: This data layer represents municipalities for Polk County, Wisconsin in 2015. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, “Polk_Municipalities_2015.gdb”.[This file includes the geographic area of each City, Village, and Town within Polk County, Wisconsin. This file was enhanced based on the standards set by GeoComm Inc. St Cloud, MN. Polk County took over the maintenance of the file in 2006. Polk County has adjusted the data to share topology in the areas where survey grade PLSS corners have been collected and to the parcel mapped areas.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
